{"title":"fix(remediation): increase mem-load memory limit to prevent OOMKilled restarts","body":"Root cause: The mem-load container's memory limit (32Mi) is insufficient for the stress command which attempts to allocate 50M of memory, causing repeated OOMKilled restarts.

Evidence: Back-off restarting failed container mem-load in pod vigil-app-66f84484b8-snvnb_default(ef9fb7f1-4e30-426c-baee-db0a2fff7c9f)

Fix: Increased mem-load container memory limit from 32Mi to 64Mi."}
